            {
              "id": "features-accordion",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "accordion",
              "settings": {
                "tabs": [
                  {
                    "tab_title": "What search filters are available?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>Smart Property Widget offers comprehensive search filters including:</p><ul><li><strong>Location:</strong> Search by area, city, or region</li><li><strong>Property Type:</strong> Villa, apartment, townhouse, penthouse, etc.</li><li><strong>Listing Type:</strong> For sale, long-term rental, short-term rental</li><li><strong>Price Range:</strong> Minimum and maximum price</li><li><strong>Bedrooms & Bathrooms:</strong> Filter by number of rooms</li><li><strong>Size:</strong> Built area and plot size</li><li><strong>Features:</strong> Pool, garden, garage, sea views, etc.</li><li><strong>Reference Number:</strong> Direct property lookup</li></ul>",
                    "_id": "features-1"
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "Can visitors save their favorite properties?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>Yes! The widget includes a wishlist feature that allows visitors to save properties they're interested in. Saved properties are stored in the browser, so visitors can return later to view their favorites. You can also add a wishlist page to your website where visitors can see all their saved properties at once.</p>",
                    "_id": "features-2"
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "Does the widget support multiple languages?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>Yes, Smart Property Widget supports 16 languages including English, Spanish, German, French, Dutch, Portuguese, Italian, Russian, Swedish, Danish, Norwegian, Finnish, Polish, Czech, Romanian, and Arabic. The widget automatically detects the visitor's language or you can set a specific language for your website.</p>",
                    "_id": "features-3"
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "Can I display properties on a map?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>Yes, the widget includes an interactive map view feature. Visitors can browse properties on a map, see property markers with price tags, and click on markers to view property details. The map integrates with Google Maps to show property locations accurately.</p>",
                    "_id": "features-4"
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "Are there different display layouts available?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>Yes, the widget offers multiple display options:</p><ul><li><strong>Grid View:</strong> Display properties in a responsive grid (1-4 columns)</li><li><strong>List View:</strong> Show properties in a detailed list format</li><li><strong>Carousel:</strong> Sliding property showcase for featured listings</li><li><strong>Map View:</strong> Interactive map with property markers</li></ul><p>There are also 12 different card templates to choose from, each with a unique design style.</p>",
                    "_id": "features-5"
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "Can I show video tours and virtual tours?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>Yes! If your properties have video tours (YouTube, Vimeo) or virtual tours (Matterport, etc.), these will automatically display on the property detail page. Visitors can watch videos and explore virtual tours directly on your website without leaving the page.</p>",
                    "_id": "features-6"
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "Is there an inquiry/contact form for properties?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>Yes, each property detail page includes an inquiry form. When visitors submit an inquiry, it is sent directly to your email address. You can customize the thank you message shown after submission or redirect visitors to a custom thank you page.</p>",
                    "_id": "features-7"
                  }
                ],
