            {
              "id": "properties-accordion",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "accordion",
              "settings": {
                "tabs": [
                  {
                    "tab_title": "How are properties synced to my website?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>Properties are automatically synced from your property management system (like Resales Online, Infocasa, or other CRM systems). When you add, update, or remove a property in your CRM, the changes are automatically reflected on your website. No manual updates required!</p>",
                    "_id": "props-1"
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "Can I feature specific properties on my homepage?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>Yes! You can display specific properties by filtering based on various criteria like location, property type, price range, or by marking properties as \"featured\" in your CRM. You can also create dedicated pages for specific property categories (e.g., \"Luxury Villas in Marbella\").</p>",
                    "_id": "props-2"
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "How many properties can I display?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>There is no limit to the number of properties you can display. Whether you have 10 properties or 10,000, the widget handles them efficiently with pagination and lazy loading to ensure fast page performance.</p>",
                    "_id": "props-3"
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "Can visitors share properties on social media?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>Yes, property detail pages include social sharing buttons that allow visitors to share properties on Facebook, Twitter, WhatsApp, LinkedIn, and via email. This helps increase exposure for your listings through word-of-mouth sharing.</p>",
                    "_id": "props-4"
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "What property information is displayed?",
                    "tab_content": "<p>Property detail pages can display comprehensive information including:</p><ul><li>Photo gallery with fullscreen view</li><li>Price and property reference</li><li>Location with interactive map</li><li>Bedrooms, bathrooms, and size details</li><li>Full property description</li><li>Features and amenities list</li><li>Video tour and virtual tour</li><li>PDF brochure download</li><li>Similar/related properties</li><li>Contact/inquiry form</li></ul>",
                    "_id": "props-5"
                  }
                ],
